# Refinement of AI Interaction & UX

This plan addresses three specific requests to refine the user experience and AI interaction:
1. Extracting/Defining the traffic generation prompt.
2. Removing the autocomplete feature.
3. Implementing dynamic thinking process prompts to replace the static loading message.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> The thinking process prompts will be generated dynamically by an AI request. This may add a slight overhead to the initial request.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend
- **Mock Data prompt:** Externalize the traffic generation logic into a prompt:
  ```markdown
  Generate mock advertisement traffic data for [CAMPAIGN_NAME]. 
  Include daily records for the last 90 days with:
  - Clicks: based on a base CTR of 1.5-8%
  - Impressions: 100-5000 per day
  - Cost: based on a base CPC of 2000-15000 VND
  - Revenue: based on a conversion rate of 0.5-5.0% and AOV of 200k-5M VND
  Apply weekend seasonality (0.9x impressions) and daily variance (0.7-1.3x).
  ```
- **Thinking Prompt API:** Create `POST /api/chat/thinking` to generate 10 "fake thinking" steps (e.g., "Analyzing campaign structure...", "Identifying top performing keywords...").

### Frontend
- **Remove Autocomplete:** 
    - [DELETE] [useAutocomplete.js](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/hooks/useAutocomplete.js)
    - [DELETE] [AutocompleteDropdown.jsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/components/chat/AutocompleteDropdown.jsx)
    - [MODIFY] [ChatInput.jsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/components/chat/ChatInput.jsx) to remove all autocomplete logic.
- **Dynamic Thinking UI:**
    - [MODIFY] [ThinkingIndicator.jsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/components/agent/ThinkingIndicator.jsx) to accept an array of 10 prompts and cycle through them every 1.5 seconds.
    - [MODIFY] [ChatPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/pages/ChatPage.jsx) to fetch these prompts from the backend when a request starts.

### Documentation
- **PRD:** Update section 4.3 (UX) and 3.1 (AI Chat) to reflect the removal of autocomplete and addition of dynamic thinking states.
- **SRS:** Update the message flow to include the "Thinking" state generation.

